template.name: Add SFDC Contact
template.desc: Displays and adds records in Tim Panagos SFDC developer account

flow.name: Add Records
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI">
  <process id="addRecords" name="Add Records" isExecutable="true">
    <startEvent id="startevent1" name="Start"/>
    <serviceTask id="task1" name="List Objects" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_list_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${listMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <userTask id="usertask1" name="Show Record" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_add_form"/>
    <serviceTask id="task4" name="Update Record" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_create_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${createMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <userTask id="usertask4" name="Confirmation" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_confirm_form">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:formProperty id="Status" name="Status" type="string" expression="${wf_status}" writable="false"/>
      </extensionElements>
    </userTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow1" sourceRef="startevent1" targetRef="task1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="done" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow9" sourceRef="usertask1" targetRef="task4"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow10" sourceRef="task4" targetRef="servicetask1"/>
    <endEvent id="endevent1" name="End"/>
    <exclusiveGateway id="exclusivegateway1" name="Exclusive Gateway" default="done"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="more" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="task4">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == "more"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow14" sourceRef="usertask4" targetRef="exclusivegateway1"/>
    <serviceTask id="servicetask1" name="List Objects" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_list_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${listMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow15" sourceRef="servicetask1" targetRef="usertask4"/>
    <serviceTask id="servicetask2" name="Read Dummy Object" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_get_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow16" sourceRef="task1" targetRef="servicetask2"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow17" sourceRef="servicetask2" targetRef="usertask1"/>
  </process>
  <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_addRecords">
    <bpmndi:BPMNPlane bpmnElement="addRecords" id="BPMNPlane_addRecords">
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="startevent1" id="BPMNShape_startevent1">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="250.0" y="50.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="task1" id="BPMNShape_task1">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="330.0" y="40.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="usertask1" id="BPMNShape_usertask1">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="330.0" y="181.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="task4" id="BPMNShape_task4">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="330.0" y="250.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="usertask4" id="BPMNShape_usertask4">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="330.0" y="410.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="endevent1" id="BPMNShape_endevent1">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="660.0" y="420.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="exclusivegateway1" id="BPMNShape_exclusivegateway1">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="40.0" width="40.0" x="540.0" y="417.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="servicetask1" id="BPMNShape_servicetask1">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="330.0" y="326.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="servicetask2" id="BPMNShape_servicetask2">
        <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="330.0" y="110.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow1" id="BPMNEdge_flow1">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="285.0" y="67.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="330.0" y="67.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="done" id="BPMNEdge_done">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="580.0" y="437.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="660.0" y="437.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow9" id="BPMNEdge_flow9">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="236.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="250.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow10" id="BPMNEdge_flow10">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="305.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="326.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="more" id="BPMNEdge_more">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="560.0" y="417.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="560.0" y="276.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="435.0" y="277.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow14" id="BPMNEdge_flow14">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="435.0" y="437.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="540.0" y="437.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow15" id="BPMNEdge_flow15">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="381.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="410.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow16" id="BPMNEdge_flow16">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="95.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="110.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow17" id="BPMNEdge_flow17">
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="165.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint x="382.0" y="181.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
    </bpmndi:BPMNPlane>
  </bpmndi:BPMNDiagram>
</definitions>
